Overview:
The Loan Application Bot is an AI-powered assistant that streamlines loan applications for borrowers and lenders. It supports personal, auto, and mortgage loans, enabling eligibility checks, loan comparisons, pre-qualification, document submission, and payment calculations. Using ScaleDown, documents are compressed by up to 80%, speeding up the process and reducing underwriter workload.

Key Features:

Loan Comparison: Compare interest rates, terms, and fees across products.

Eligibility Calculator: Calculates maximum loan based on income, credit, and expenses.

Pre-Qualification: AI-driven assessment in under 2 minutes.

Document Management: Upload, auto-tag, and compress documents.

Application Tracking: Real-time status updates.

Payment Calculator: EMI and interest calculation for informed decisions.

Rate Monitoring: Tracks changing interest rates for optimal loan selection.

Architecture:

Frontend: Web or chatbot interface for user interaction

Backend: Python + FastAPI/Flask, handles loan calculations and NLP

ScaleDown: Compresses uploaded documents for faster processing

Database: Stores users, loans, applications, and documents

Analytics: Tracks approval rate, pre-qualification time, and satisfaction

Workflow:

User starts chat and selects loan type.

Bot collects financial info and estimates eligibility.

Compares loan options and calculates EMIs.

Users upload documents; ScaleDown compresses them.

Application is submitted and tracked; analytics update dashboard.

Unique Features:

Smart Loan Advisor: Personalized loan suggestions.

AI Document Tagging: Auto-classifies uploaded files.

Dashboard Analytics: Tracks key metrics for lenders and borrowers.
